Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.19,0:00:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.79,0:00:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在大家都静静睡下的夜晚\Nみんなが寝静まった夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从窗口眺望夜空的话\N窓から空を見ていると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.69,0:00:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以看到很厉害的东西\Nとっても　すごいものを　見たんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人们都笑者说\N大人は誰も笑いながら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我电视看太多了\Nテレビの見過ぎと言うけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我绝对绝对\N僕は　絶対に絶対に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会说谎\N嘘なんか言ってない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.79,0:00:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不会用名为常识的眼镜\N常識と言う眼鏡で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.19,0:00:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我们的世界\N僕たちの世界は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.59,0:00:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进行窥视\Nのぞけやしないのさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.59,0:00:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘记了梦想的\N夢を忘れた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.59,0:01:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古老的地球人啊\N古い地球人よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.59,0:01:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好奇妙的感觉\N不思議な気持ち
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.93,0:01:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.75,0:01:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十四話 幻影殖民地 上集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.85,0:01:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.94,0:01:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失禮了\n不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.23,0:02:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是修理的經過報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.01,0:02:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個放在艦橋就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.19,0:02:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想早點讓你看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.25,0:02:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前我們處於食物和資源不足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.15,0:02:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能早點找到補給基地總是好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.68,0:02:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.32,0:02:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開什麼玩笑,你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.32,0:02:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看螢幕就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.90,0:02:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在拉比安羅茲很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.46,0:02:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.74,0:02:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好大的隕石群阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.30,0:02:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是假隕石嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.04,0:02:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,剛才本來想避開的\n可是不知不覺中被包圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.89,0:02:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長,你來的太遲了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.64,0:02:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.48,0:02:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉比安羅茲那邊有什麼情報嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.01,0:02:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我確認看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.17,0:02:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.62,0:02:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣根本就救不出莉娜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.44,0:02:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.10,0:02:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去分析看看螢幕中央的隕石\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.60,0:02:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些是假隕石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.84,0:02:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是並不是氣球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.27,0:02:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,質量很大的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.93,0:03:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把影像擴大到最大\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.77,0:03:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是戰艦嘛?\n不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.88,0:03:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長,這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.92,0:03:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是設立最初的\n史威特型殖民地的空域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.12,0:03:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經被遺棄很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.19,0:03:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是放棄開發的殖民地嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.79,0:03:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.69,0:03:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說這裏是暗礁空域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.07,0:03:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是禍不單行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.38,0:03:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&Hedd8ad&}外部的人們,你們聽的見嗎{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.81,0:03:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什麼?特雷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.30,0:03:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.26,0:03:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是用舊式電波發出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.66,0:03:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是亞古捷斯,不是奧干\n也不是泰暗坦斯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.02,0:03:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是從那垃圾堆中發出來的電波嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.46,0:03:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&Hedd8ad&}我們是住在月月的光之族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.01,0:03:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&Hedd8ad&}我們一直等候個位的造訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.12,0:03:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&Hedd8ad&}各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.31,0:03:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&Hedd8ad&}必需到我們的殖民地來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.19,0:03:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼光之族?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.94,0:03:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&Hedd8ad&}只要我們團結起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.17,0:03:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&Hedd8ad&}一切都會往好的方向發展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.93,0:03:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是在說安多拉嗎?布拉度先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.20,0:03:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.36,0:03:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾美莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.27,0:04:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉比安羅茲的資料裏頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.22,0:04:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曾提過那是支持\n獨立主義的殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.55,0:04:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以去補給物資嗎?\n是,可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.33,0:04:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好去了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.59,0:04:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.94,0:04:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵從對方指示,特雷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.09,0:04:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是...是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.86,0:04:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光之族,亞加瑪知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.42,0:04:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&Hedd8ad&}你們好像有兩艘船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.87,0:04:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&Hedd8ad&}白色的船到月月來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.81,0:04:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&Hedd8ad&}這是命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.72,0:04:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,入口很狹小,小心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.83,0:04:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們想幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.79,0:04:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方自稱光之族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.06,0:04:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼知道他們是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.96,0:04:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那又怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.23,0:05:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想在殖民地內戰鬥嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.75,0:05:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在香格里拉就幹過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.84,0:05:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,殖民地的大小差太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.60,0:05:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉,別亂來\n我們不會開戰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.36,0:05:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉度艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.63,0:05:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是宇宙時代前的服裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.99,0:05:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們誤闖過去了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.77,0:05:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.64,0:05:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟莎拉莎大人說的一樣\n有巨神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.42,0:05:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破壞這巨神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.04,0:05:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巨神開動的話,會危害月月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.60,0:05:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是安多拉的手下嗎?\n不准動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.02,0:05:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛 好大的巨神阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.87,0:06:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是特別危險的巨神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該用炸彈破壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.42,0:06:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這麼做連港口都會壞掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.89,0:06:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.95,0:06:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷靜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.07,0:06:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個MS不是你們想的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.25,0:06:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來到月月的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.87,0:06:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就應該遵從光之族的預言書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.69,0:06:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.18,0:06:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們知不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.44,0:06:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在是什麼時代了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.29,0:06:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,破壞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.18,0:06:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.57,0:06:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與其讓別人破壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.88,0:06:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如我們自己分解吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.74,0:06:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分解...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.42,0:06:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了,我們自己動手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.94,0:06:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎,你很明理阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.32,0:06:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會被看出破綻吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.28,0:06:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些年輕人看起來很果斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.05,0:06:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!可能是莎拉莎大人\n期待的年輕人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.32,0:06:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?為什麼分散ZZ高達?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.28,0:06:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在做什麼阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.51,0:06:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巨神被破壞了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.60,0:07:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿斯蘭治!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.67,0:07:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要拆開ZZ高達??\n為什麼阿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.46,0:07:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他叫我們破壞ZZ高達,所以才...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.45,0:07:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那實在太遺憾了..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.49,0:07:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長,這是怎麼一回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.66,0:07:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.72,0:07:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.45,0:07:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.65,0:07:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾美莉,是這樣的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.53,0:07:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的神阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.41,0:07:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣他們應該接受了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.12,0:07:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在就下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.09,0:07:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們克制悲傷\n瓦解掉一個巨神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.92,0:07:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你們也答應我們的請求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.34,0:07:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們直接與教祖談吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.08,0:07:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她應該會見你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.36,0:08:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家別再哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.55,0:08:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們必須克服悲傷\n做我們非做不可的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.95,0:08:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.78,0:08:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.70,0:08:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.66,0:08:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒看到捷度阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.27,0:08:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.20,0:08:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不可以過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.63,0:08:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.66,0:08:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有港口艙門才有電氣機關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.92,0:08:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,電氣機關...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.34,0:08:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了被選上的戰士之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.70,0:08:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一般人是不許接觸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.69,0:08:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是月月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是殖民地阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.26,0:08:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.00,0:08:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常感謝你們進入月月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.80,0:08:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,助我們一臂之力\n不勝感激...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.71,0:09:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裏?我打仗打累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.30,0:09:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想要喘個氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.53,0:09:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光之族不使用武器\n非常令人敬佩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.99,0:09:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們願意出力幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.03,0:09:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們光之族達成目的嗎?是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.97,0:09:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就請對神殿外部的凱多魯誓忠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.68,0:09:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣我們就是同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.70,0:09:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把身心獻給月光與日光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.50,0:09:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,願宇宙中不再有戰鬥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.76,0:09:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何陪他們玩這個遊戲?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.69,0:09:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜喜歡,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.21,0:09:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只好配合了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.00,0:09:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的\n就請你們準備幫助我們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.70,0:09:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先讓我們參觀殖民地內部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.67,0:09:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣太冒險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.12,0:09:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們已經做好準備了,隨時可讓\n姬娜小姐滿意,怎樣?客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.14,0:09:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.71,0:09:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.54,0:09:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只是要拖時間\n等古利明帶新戰艦過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.24,0:10:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜歡綠地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.88,0:10:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,莫迪,你們也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.32,0:10:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好美麗,是哪裏人阿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.16,0:10:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我那麼美嗎?\n當然美啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.83,0:10:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.54,0:10:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.49,0:10:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要喝杯茶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.01,0:10:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜呢?\n糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.43,0:10:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.68,0:10:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.80,0:10:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是說阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.25,0:10:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.84,0:10:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你不是美女的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.61,0:10:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不會跟來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.87,0:10:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.19,0:10:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你綁架人的,你還害羞?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.58,0:10:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別欺負人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.41,0:10:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個人我見過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.87,0:10:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那女人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.95,0:10:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個紅髮女人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.69,0:10:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒帶錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.28,0:10:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是進入另一邊港口的\n船上的女人...過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.20,0:10:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待在殖民地內部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.21,0:10:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最能刺激我的野性之心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.84,0:11:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?不要...放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.22,0:11:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口\n可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.50,0:11:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上馬車了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.54,0:11:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追上去吧,我去通知戈圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.25,0:11:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我們加入光之族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.47,0:11:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,只要你們誓忠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.99,0:11:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就全力協助你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.65,0:11:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,補給的事也沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.59,0:11:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只是要獵得物質罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.61,0:11:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會付錢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.11,0:11:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.38,0:11:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不服從的話\n我也沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.28,0:11:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想利用我們的船做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.61,0:11:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們需要宇宙船,讓我們把光之教\n的教義傳播到全宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.46,0:11:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生大事了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.62,0:11:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.06,0:11:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安多拉的姬娜小姐\n被叛亂者抓走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.96,0:11:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安多拉?你接觸敵對的兩批人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.66,0:11:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,未免太過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.51,0:11:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果能夠知道救世主\n是坐在哪艘船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.09,0:12:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們當然不會這麼做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.53,0:12:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個是教祖的神殿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.46,0:12:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在等候救世主?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.38,0:12:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,那是為了將光之教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.92,0:12:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的教義傳播到全宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.68,0:12:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以需要我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.94,0:12:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的安多拉與亞加瑪嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.14,0:12:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就知道你這麼美\n一定會瞭解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.12,0:12:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我美麗?!你說話真討人歡心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.65,0:12:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光之教的教義是教人回歸自然是吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.50,0:12:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是好事阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.91,0:12:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是外面世界的爭端\n一直沒停止過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.50,0:12:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光之族到宇宙去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.49,0:12:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月月可能就會喪失和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.77,0:12:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,教祖他們不瞭解這點阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.77,0:12:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,那些騙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.70,0:13:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想以姬娜大人為人質\n將安多拉出賣給亞加碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.66,0:13:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.73,0:13:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會讓我當正規軍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.99,0:13:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,就利用那個小ㄚ頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.60,0:13:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正古利明不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.25,0:13:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫莉娜去薩克C上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.57,0:13:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜?這樣太...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.75,0:13:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辦不到的話你就不用當軍人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.77,0:13:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薩克C能出動吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.60,0:13:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜給你們當人質\n守在安多拉周圍的原始人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.44,0:13:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就用瓦斯催眠他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.32,0:13:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.36,0:13:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們作法太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.75,0:13:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手,來救人阿,哥哥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.69,0:13:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們對弱女子做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.01,0:13:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們想做什麼?\n出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.83,0:13:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這地方有巨神\n他們詐欺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.31,0:13:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們做這種事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.57,0:13:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不怕我跟古利明告密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.30,0:13:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他已經出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.20,0:13:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巨神動起來了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.77,0:13:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!莉娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.46,0:13:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰來救我啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.49,0:13:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經盡力了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.38,0:14:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想個辦法的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.30,0:14:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔...!對了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.64,0:14:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥,救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.20,0:14:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.54,0:14:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.13,0:14:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手阿\n別用MS在殖民地裏面鬧事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.84,0:14:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殖民地裏面?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.77,0:14:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽到妹妹的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.45,0:14:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妹妹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.40,0:14:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,被你們抓走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.65,0:14:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是古利明干的,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.85,0:14:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你拜託艦長放了莉娜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.88,0:14:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.09,0:14:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道安多拉的艦長很亂來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.94,0:14:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你長的這麼美\n應該能說服他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.49,0:14:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這倒也不是辦不到...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.68,0:14:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的目的是救出姬娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.47,0:14:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏的人也擁有武器\n小心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.61,0:15:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手,是誰在上面駕駛的?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.39,0:15:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要找出姬娜\n跟她討一個公道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.60,0:15:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薩克C隊\n你們到神殿的山丘恐嚇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.03,0:15:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有人去鎮壓神殿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.43,0:15:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自轉的怪車過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.40,0:15:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.18,0:15:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薩克C
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.75,0:15:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是莉娜,莉娜在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.51,0:15:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,你利用部下...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.29,0:15:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這麼美,才不會這麼卑鄙\n是戈圖干的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.85,0:15:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巨神凱爾特阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.84,0:15:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是凱爾特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.42,0:15:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是外部世界的機器人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.25,0:15:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱爾特?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.22,0:15:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這裏的神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.90,0:16:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我帶你妹妹回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.97,0:16:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是為了證明我的美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.08,0:16:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎?她要放了莉娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.71,0:16:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你掛在那邊好久,累了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.04,0:16:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你注意到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.47,0:16:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許我需要你的幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.93,0:16:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這...好美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.29,0:16:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戈圖,你...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.39,0:16:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼不顧慮到殖民地的安危?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.67,0:16:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你染污神殿想做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.50,0:16:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們都聯合起來了還裝蒜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.31,0:16:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不把姬娜大人還回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.07,0:16:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就要鎮壓這個殖民地!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.29,0:16:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不懂你在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.84,0:16:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別裝蒜了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.22,0:16:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停下來,薩克C,停下來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.95,0:16:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個笨蛋,我叫你看這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.15,0:16:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.04,0:16:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巨神說話了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.19,0:16:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.18,0:16:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人,你怎麼在那裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.58,0:17:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伸手過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.66,0:17:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是莉娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.42,0:17:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.63,0:17:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去船上!\n遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.10,0:17:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戈圖!戈圖!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.80,0:17:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜!我妹妹呢,莉娜啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.31,0:17:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是...?是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.61,0:17:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.73,0:17:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是MS阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.71,0:17:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有不好的預感!快追上姬娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.67,0:17:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們沒時間怕了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.05,0:17:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡,這樣會引起殖民地混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.81,0:17:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長又不連絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.02,0:17:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度他們也失去音訊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.36,0:17:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧,艾利,伊萊\n瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.55,0:17:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能成功嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.86,0:17:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薩克C,停下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.86,0:17:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向神殿前往的薩克C給我停下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.62,0:18:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人!\n姬娜大人,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.77,0:18:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把綁在薩克C上面的女孩放下來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.44,0:18:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?\n為什麼?那是因為...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.71,0:18:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安多拉果然動手了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.38,0:18:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼我要就那個女孩呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.70,0:18:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好大的聲音阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.34,0:18:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼想挑戰嗎!\n好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.35,0:18:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏不是MS打鬥的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.60,0:18:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,不可以攻擊姬娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.73,0:18:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有武器!\n有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.29,0:18:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼!\n煙霧彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.84,0:18:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些傢伙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.44,0:19:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是敵人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.45,0:19:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是RJJ!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.54,0:19:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰運過去的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.08,0:19:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人,RJJ是送給你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.61,0:19:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你派人送來的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.53,0:19:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快把位子讓給姬娜大人!\n你會被殺死的  是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.66,0:19:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來了,這是我的RJJ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.29,0:19:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去了哪裏?ZZ高達躲在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.98,0:19:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點找出ZZ高達!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.54,0:19:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.02,0:19:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.76,0:19:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交給你了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.97,0:19:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜!你要等我啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.06,0:19:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要合體了,聽見了沒有?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.41,0:19:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解了!\n瞭解了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.34,0:20:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.12,0:20:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把妹妹還給我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.73,0:20:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了!ZZ高達出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.06,0:20:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.18,0:20:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.83,0:20:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜,在那個MS裏的人是你嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.82,0:20:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是答應\n要放了莉娜的嗎?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.73,0:20:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告訴你,我是不會放過在身邊的任何MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.12,0:20:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去神殿會被毀掉的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.55,0:20:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人處於危險狀態...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.80,0:20:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對MS們發下撤退命令\n遵命!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.20,0:20:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉杜艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.69,0:20:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度沒看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.51,0:20:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜被當作人質嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.27,0:20:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜!放手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.73,0:20:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達!\n你只要與我決鬥就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.69,0:20:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又害到莉娜遇到危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.97,0:21:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜,快逃!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.62,0:21:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點程度的損傷不算什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.64,0:21:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快逃走!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.75,0:21:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個MS已經要死了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.77,0:21:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死了?RJJ死了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.29,0:21:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,控制那個巨神的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.62,0:21:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是月月的救世主!\n救世主出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.90,0:21:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度是救世主?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.66,0:21:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個女人連神殿都想破壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.62,0:21:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...我是...對不起,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.39,0:21:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會原諒我吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.01,0:21:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情發生了也沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.49,0:21:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多寬大的胸襟阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.12,0:21:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是救世主!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.16,0:21:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要這樣,我不是救世主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.49,0:21:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的名子叫做捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.20,0:22:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼捷度\n我要拜託你一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.09,0:22:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有求於人的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.09,0:22:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別無禮!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.07,0:22:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.85,0:22:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你再做什麼?拉莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.08,0:22:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼一回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.41,0:22:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉?我不是拉莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.57,0:22:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是莎拉莎.月,統治光之族的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.16,0:22:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,教祖...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.10,0:22:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在没有道路的荒野里\N道もない荒れた原野に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.10,0:22:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建造铁路真是一件辛苦差事\Nレールを作るのは苦しいことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.10,0:23:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\Nだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.50,0:23:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以不知晓远方\N遠い向こうも知らなくちゃいけない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.70,0:23:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我们的路现在才开始\N僕達は これからなんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.80,0:23:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们都说我们是“忘记了梦想的小孩子”\N“夢を忘れた子供達”と 人は言う
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.50,0:23:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊啊 时代正在哭泣\Nああー 時代が泣いている
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.58,0:23:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果 我們被關進了月月的牢房 那麼就要逃跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.85,0:23:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃跑之後 蒙德遇見拉莎拉小姐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.64,0:23:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們為了奪回ZZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.02,0:23:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和叛徒們一起工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.63,0:24:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後 那個古利明又回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.37,0:24:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想帶走莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.55,0:24:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下集 高達ZZ 幻影殖民地 下集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.80,0:24:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是今天的繼續

